- Turn on the stove for the oil.
- Did you turn on the stove?

313
00:09:54,863 --> 00:09:55,933
I'll do it.

314
00:09:56,033 --> 00:09:57,402
- Turn on the stove for the oil.
- Did you turn on the stove?

315
00:09:57,403 --> 00:09:58,433
I'll do it.

316
