- Okay?

329
00:10:21,253 --> 00:10:22,692
- That's good.
- Is this good?

330
00:10:22,693 --> 00:10:23,722
- Yes.
- Put it in here?

331
00:10:23,723 --> 00:10:25,223
Put that in there and add sesame oil.

332
00:10:25,693 --> 00:10:26,992
