A drop of sesame oil.

2521
01:28:51,498 --> 01:28:53,034
(Black seabream sushi is complete with a single drop of sesame oil.)

2522
01:28:53,058 --> 01:28:54,498
This must be the taste of the devil.

2523
01:28:54,998 --> 01:28:56,028
My goodness.

2524
01:28:56,168 --> 01:28:58,338
- Jong Min.
- My goodness. Thank you.

2525
01:28:58,798 --> 01:29:00,437
(The sushi that he simply cannot refuse today)

2526
01:29:00,438 --> 01:29:02,438
- I'm honored.
- It looks really delicious.

2527
01:29:02,638 --> 01:29:05,108
- My gosh.
- I bet it's great.

2528
01:29:06,638 --> 01:29:08,047
(It looks delicious.)

2529
01:29:08,048 --> 01:29:09,048
It must be amazing.

2530
01:29:09,049 --> 01:29:10,078
(Exclaiming)

2531
01:29:11,578 --> 01:29:13,218
- My gosh.
- How is it, Jong Min?

2532
01:29:14,018 --> 01:29:16,248
- It goes crazy in my mouth.
- Is it crazy?

2533
01:29:17,318 --> 01:29:19,258
I think it's my turn.

2534
01:29:19,358 --> 01:29:20,988
He gets the delicious part.

2535
01:29:21,928 --> 01:29:23,387
Right. The double belly sushi.

2536
01:29:23,388 --> 01:29:25,227
The double belly. I can feel his love.

2537
01:29:25,228 --> 01:29:27,528
This piece of kimchi should be mine.

2538
01:29:27,898 --> 01:29:29,868
I'll eat it here right away. Thank you.

2539
01:29:30,238 --> 01:29:32,468
(Giant black seabream belly sushi befitting Se Yoon)

2540
01:29:32,768 --> 01:29:34,308
(Putting it into his mouth)

2541
01:29:37,508 --> 01:29:39,238
This is amazing.

2542
01:29:39,408 --> 01:29:42,007
(Putting it into his partner, Sam Kim's mouth, too)

2543
01:29:42,008 --> 01:29:44,177
I'm sorry to say this, but it can't even be compared...

2544
01:29:44,178 --> 01:29:45,448
to rockfish or flatfish.

2545
01:29:45,978 --> 01:29:48,147
- The texture...
- The texture is amazing.

2546
01:29:48,148 --> 01:29:50,588
(He finally tries the black seabream that he sliced himself.)

2547
01:29:51,188 --> 01:29:52,288
The sashimi is really good.

2548
01:29:52,488 --> 01:29:53,727
It feels like gum.

2549
01:29:53,728 --> 01:29:56,728
It keeps making the chomping sound in my mouth.

2550
01:29:57,928 --> 01:29:59,097
(He adds as many pieces of sashimi as he wants.)

2551
01:29:59,098 --> 01:30:01,167
What? Are you making sashimi bibimbap?

2552
01:30:01,168 --> 01:30:03,498
(He mixes it well to make sashimi bibimbap.)

2553
01:30:03,638 --> 01:30:05,037
That's expensive sashimi bibimbap.

2554
01:30:05,038 --> 01:30:06,697
- Can I try this?
- Yes. Have a spoonful each.

2555
01:30:06,698 --> 01:30:09,058
I can't believe I'm eating black seabream sashimi bibimbap.

2556
01:30:09,108 --> 01:30:10,108
My goodness.

2557
01:30:11,808 --> 01:30:16,808
(The taste perfected by the large black seabream)

2558
01:30:18,778 --> 01:30:20,988
(They can't stop eating.)

2559
01:30:22,948 --> 01:30:24,958
The sauce is perfectly balanced.

2560
01:30:25,258 --> 01:30:26,258
My gosh.

2561
01:30:27,188 --> 01:30:29,727
Gosh, it's strange, but the fish tastes sweet.

2562
01:30:29,728 --> 01:30:30,797
- It's sweet, isn't it?
- Yes.

2563
01:30:30,798 --> 01:30:31,958
It's not strange.

2564
01:30:32,658 --> 01:30:33,667
(He holds back his laughter by drinking some soup.)

2565
01:30:33,668 --> 01:30:34,698
All his dishes are sweet.

2566
01:30:34,828 --> 01:30:36,467
(Sugar Hands Jung Ho Young makes even sashimi sweet.)

2567
01:30:36,468 --> 01:30:37,938
Even the sashimi is sweet.

2568
01:30:38,638 --> 01:30:40,607
Thank you so much, Ho Young.

2569
01:30:40,608 --> 01:30:42,168
Thank you for this amazing breakfast.

2570
01:30:42,568 --> 01:30:44,178
It tastes best when we share food.

2571
01:30:45,008 --> 01:30:47,347
(I agree.)

2572
01:30:47,348 --> 01:30:48,607
So, today...

2573
01:30:48,608 --> 01:30:50,648
How was it? Wasn't our show too tough?

2574
01:30:50,818 --> 01:30:53,448
It would be a lie to say it wasn't tough,

2575
01:30:53,578 --> 01:30:56,718
but it was really fun. I feel like I just laughed until the end.

2576
01:30:57,888 --> 01:30:59,688
(He showed up arm in arm with his partner...)

2577
01:30:59,888 --> 01:31:01,968
(and first met the members with a fluttering heart.)

2578
01:31:03,488 --> 01:31:05,098
(He was a little clumsy at games, )

2579
01:31:05,198 --> 01:31:07,198
(but he showed his passion that spared no effort.)

2580
01:31:07,728 --> 01:31:10,228
(He couldn't hide his dance instincts.)

2581
01:31:10,668 --> 01:31:13,268
(He's a pro game-enjoyer who knows how to enjoy himself.)

2582
01:31:13,538 --> 01:31:14,768
He's going to salvage...

2583
01:31:15,068 --> 01:31:18,008
(He brings even dead dishes back to life.)

2584
01:31:18,938 --> 01:31:21,347
(A chef who knows no danger, at least when cooking)

2585
01:31:21,348 --> 01:31:23,408
I didn't know the day would be this short.

2586
01:31:24,478 --> 01:31:26,918
- How nice.
- I had a great time here.

2587
01:31:26,948 --> 01:31:28,887
I enjoyed nature.

2588
01:31:28,888 --> 01:31:30,487
This is something we don't usually get to enjoy.

2589
01:31:30,488 --> 01:31:32,088
I could do it thanks to 2 Days 1 Night.

2590
01:31:32,558 --> 01:31:33,558
(Amazed)

2591
01:31:34,328 --> 01:31:35,958
(It feels like a foreign country.)

2592
01:31:36,528 --> 01:31:39,198
(He set off with emotion, escaping his repetitive days.)

2593
01:31:40,228 --> 01:31:43,228
(In the wild variety show where nothing was easy, )

2594
01:31:45,038 --> 01:31:47,938
(he had a series of tough competitions, )

2595
01:31:48,168 --> 01:31:50,728
(but Sam Kim is a genius chef when it comes to cooking battles.)

2596
01:31:50,808 --> 01:31:53,328
(With his Italian dish that captivated everyone's taste buds, )

2597
01:31:53,678 --> 01:31:57,717
(he claimed a victory sweeter than ever.)

2598
01:31:57,718 --> 01:31:59,547
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

2599
01:31:59,548 --> 01:32:01,017
- We enjoyed your dishes.
- Thank you.

2600
01:32:01,018 --> 01:32:03,564
(We thank Chefs Jung Ho Young and Sam Kim for joining us for 2 days.)

2601
01:32:03,588 --> 01:32:05,818
(Thanks to them, we had a delicious 2 Days 1 Night.)

2602
01:32:06,358 --> 01:32:08,987
Is it even allowed to be this delicious?

2603
01:32:08,988 --> 01:32:10,027
Halibut!

2604
01:32:10,028 --> 01:32:12,558
Is this the taste of Mokpo?

2605
01:32:12,658 --> 01:32:13,698
Webfoot octopus!

2606
01:32:13,898 --> 01:32:15,167
A city of gastronomy.

2607
01:32:15,168 --> 01:32:16,697
Come visit Mokpo.

2608
01:32:16,698 --> 01:32:17,967
Korea's best...

2609
01:32:17,968 --> 01:32:19,797
Real wild road variety show!

2610
01:32:19,798 --> 01:32:20,968
Who are we?

2611
01:32:21,068 --> 01:32:25,008
- 2 Days!
- 1 Night!

2612
01:32:26,738 --> 01:32:29,508
(The gourmet trip to Mokpo with Ho Young and Sam Kim is over.)

2613
01:32:29,608 --> 01:32:31,518
(Next episode)

2614
01:32:31,848 --> 01:32:33,818
(With the arrival of the languid spring)

2615
01:32:34,348 --> 01:32:37,188
(A guest who will fill 2 Days 1 Night with passion)

2616
01:32:38,188 --> 01:32:39,587
- What?
- What?

2617
01:32:39,588 --> 01:32:44,128
(U-Know Yunho is here.)

2618
01:32:44,428 --> 01:32:45,828
(And Kang Jae Jun)

2619
01:32:46,128 --> 01:32:48,227
(The most harmful bug to humans is...)

2620
01:32:48,228 --> 01:32:49,568
("half-heartedness.")

2621
01:32:50,328 --> 01:32:51,897
(Half-heartedness?)

2622
01:32:51,898 --> 01:32:53,138
(What is it?)

2623
01:32:54,638 --> 01:32:57,908
(This is 100-percent passion with no half-heartedness.)

2624
01:32:58,038 --> 01:32:59,477
(U-Know Yunho's quote)

2625
01:32:59,478 --> 01:33:02,147
(With passion alone, there is nothing you can't achieve.)

2626
01:33:02,148 --> 01:33:03,248
- Do you want it?
- Yes.

2627
01:33:03,308 --> 01:33:06,348
(An untiring passion bulldozer)

2628
01:33:06,648 --> 01:33:07,718
(Please stop it now.)

2629
01:33:08,518 --> 01:33:11,358
(For me, there is no such thing as stopping.)

2630
01:33:11,558 --> 01:33:12,758
This is tough.

2631
01:33:13,118 --> 01:33:15,988
(Just how far will his passion go?)

2632
01:33:17,758 --> 01:33:21,568
(See you next week.)
